  "informal_statement": "The number of primes less than 10 (namely 2, 3, 5, 7) is 4: ((Finset.range 10).filter Nat.Prime).card = 4.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "`decide` closes this finite, fully computable statement directly by kernel evaluation.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem primes_below_ten_card : ((Finset.range 10).filter (fun n => Nat.Prime n)).card = 4",
